Bhaavi mahimato polchutakai{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Shramayu baadha himsayainanu karuvu vastra
Heenatayunu upadravamainanu khadgamainanu
Edabaapune prabhu premanundi{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Maranamu jeevamainanu deva dootalu
Pradhanulu adikaarulu mari evarainanu
Edabaparu prabhu premanundi{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Anaadi devuni aa sankalpam manalo prabhuni
Bayalu parapa maanavalenu mana paapamulu
Poonikatho poorna aikyathaku{/lang-eng}
